{"tid":490304,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"【Orage台】普通閒聊 Day155 5/12","createTime":"2017-12-05T13:27:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-05T15:37:30.000Z","uid":122942,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"789a1f9a822b957132a78c22b214586d985ee334","tid":490304,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T13:27:38.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/5ADqP2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2F5ADqP2.gif&h=8c5a58f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大家好，我係Orage。 我會於每晚11點至2點開台玩遊戲同與觀眾聊天。<br />\n因為我極度3分鐘熱度，所以好少會一直玩同一隻Game。<br />\n有興趣嘅巴打入黎捧下場，一齊傾下計啦  <br />\n<br />\n今晚9點左右見 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.twitch.tv/oragejan \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.twitch.tv%2Foragejan%20&d=72kWLAB6SYRy9AS2Al0Q%2FF0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=e9eb6037\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.twitch.tv/oragejan </a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/W4CK8P.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FW4CK8P.png&h=69cccb5f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n另外我開左個FB專頁，有時會PO日常野同覺得有趣嘅事，<br />\n希望巴打們可以入黎比個讚。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/oragejan\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Foragejan&d=72kWLAB6SYRy9AS2Al0Q%2FF0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=52700ac0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/oragejan</a></div>"},{"pid":"b68d3cb9c9bf2295fbf0304c8f6cb0c723bbf5d9","tid":490304,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T13:36:05.000Z","msg":"已開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ae17dbe91bcf69f16b8a4a77b9e7aaf5c952c83","tid":490304,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T13:36:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85769d1375c7a172a19adf575101311e1435dfb9","tid":490304,"